Start the back end first then run this from the frontend dir:
docker build -t my-react-app .
docker run -p 3000:80 my-react-app
http://localhost:3000

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Needed sometimes if fails to run:
docker build -t my-react-app .
docker run --rm --name usnrl-weather-router-frontend -p 3000:80 my-react-app
http://localhost:3000